name: The Temptress
description:
Forbidden Fruit

She draws you in, 
from her pretty lips breaths hell into your ear. 
“Tie me up.”
“Take me now.”
“Claim my body as yours.”
For it's then she truly has control.

Feels like heaven. 
Tastes like sin.
“Worship my body.”
“Kiss every curve.”
“Take me in.”

-Kassandra Complex

Wonderfully eerie collaboration with the amazing and the talented Sexfractals 
Twitter: @sexfractals
